Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.28,0:18:47.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里好像是迪奥下车的地方…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.95,0:18:50.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们一起来的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.71,0:18:52.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.54,0:18:54.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 瞒着你
