Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.35,0:19:10.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,路上碰见了 他们邀请我去购物
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.89,0:19:12.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迪奥去吃饭了？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.64,0:19:13.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.02,0:19:14.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道说…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.40,0:19:17.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和父亲一起…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.94,0:19:19.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.66,0:19:28.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么啊 那家伙
